---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_AUTHOR, SITE_EMAIL } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
  title={`Privacy Policy — ${SITE_TITLE}`}
  description="Privacy policy for Simply Useful Apps and the Galerie app."
>
  <section class="policy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">
      Applies to: Galerie for iOS<br />
      Effective date: April 9, 2026<br />
      Published by: {SITE_AUTHOR}
    </p>

    <p>
      Galerie is designed to be simple and private. This policy describes what
      data the app accesses and how it is used. The short version: your photos
      stay on your device, and analytics data we collect does not include
      personally identifiable information.
    </p>

    <h2>Photo Library</h2>
    <p>
      Galerie requests read-only access to your photo library in order to
      display your photos as a slideshow. The app does not upload, transmit,
      modify, or share your photos or any information derived from them. All
      access occurs entirely on your device.
    </p>

    <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      No account is required to use Galerie. We do not collect your name, email
      address, photo library contents, or other personally identifiable
      information.
    </p>
    <p>
      We do collect limited usage analytics to understand app quality and
      feature usage. This includes technical and aggregate data such as app
      version, device model, operating system version, locale, and session
      activity.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Galerie uses TelemetryDeck, a privacy-focused analytics provider, to
      process limited app analytics on our behalf. We configure analytics so
      that personally identifiable information is not included in analytics
      signals.
    </p>
    <p>
      Analytics are used only to improve reliability and usability. We do not
      use analytics for advertising, profiling, or selling personal data.
    </p>
    <p>
      TelemetryDeck's privacy policy is available at
      <a href="https://telemetrydeck.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        telemetrydeck.com/privacy
      </a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      In-app purchases are processed by Apple through the App Store. We do not
      receive or store any payment information. Apple's privacy policy governs
      that transaction and can be found at
      <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        apple.com/legal/privacy
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Galerie does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information
      from children under the age of 13.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this page
      with a revised effective date. We encourage you to review it periodically.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this privacy policy can be sent to{' '}
      <a href={`mailto:${SITE_EMAIL}`}>{SITE_EMAIL}</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy {
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .policy h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .meta {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .policy h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .policy a {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>